{"title":"Les Flex-Box","content":"<p>Pour traiter des flex-box, qui sont un outil CSS extr\u00eamement puissant, j'ai choisi de r\u00e9aliser une vid\u00e9o explicative. Vous trouverez sous la vid\u00e9o le code html. Bon visionnage !<\/p>\n\n<video src=\"img\/res\/flex_box.mp4\" controls>Votre navigateur ne supporte pas la vid\u00e9o HTML5 !<\/video>\n\n<p>Voil\u00e0 le code pr\u00e9sent\u00e9 dans la vid\u00e9o: <\/p>\n\n<textarea>\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n    <head>\n        <style>\n            \n            body{\n                margin: 0;\n                display: flex;\n                flex-wrap: wrap;\n                justify-content: space-around;\n            }\n            img{\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n            .carte{\n                width: 200px;\n                text-align: center;\n                background-color: crimson;\n                color: white;\n                box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n                margin: 15px;\n            }\n            .carte h3{\n                margin: 0;\n                padding: 15px 0px;\n            }\n        <\/style>        \n    <\/head>\n    <body>\n        \n        <div class=\"carte\">\n            <img src=\"image.png\">\n            <h3>Mon titre<\/h3>\n        <\/div>\n        \n        <div class=\"carte\">\n            <img src=\"image.png\">\n            <h3>Mon titre<\/h3>\n        <\/div>\n        \n        <div class=\"carte\">\n            <img src=\"image.png\">\n            <h3>Mon titre<\/h3>\n        <\/div>\n        \n        <div class=\"carte\">\n            <img src=\"image.png\">\n            <h3>Mon titre<\/h3>\n        <\/div>\n        \n        <div class=\"carte\">\n            <img src=\"image.png\">\n            <h3>Mon titre<\/h3>\n        <\/div>\n        \n        <div class=\"carte\">\n            <img src=\"image.png\">\n            <h3>Mon titre<\/h3>\n        <\/div>\n        \n    <\/body>\n<\/html>\n<\/textarea>","lvl":"confirme","published":"true","id":"1497209638"}